values:
I'm just lounging in my dorm, watching Scrubs (which is an awesome show) and thinking about how great my life is right now. I know I&nbsp;complain a lot, and I&nbsp;really don't mean to make such a big deal out of little things that put me out, but I'm also not going to deny that I do it. Today, though, I feel like life is on the right track. I have a wonderful group of friends who are supportive and fun. I have a handsome, intelligent boyfriend who makes me smile all the time. I have a class schedule&nbsp;that's interesting and challenging, but not&nbsp;overwhelming.&nbsp;

I guess I just wanted to&nbsp;say, that I'm glad that everything is so good right now. That everything is going my way. And I hope everyone else feels as good as I do about life right now.
&nbsp;
